sql_query:
SELECT 
    issue_key, 
    summary, 
    status, 
    duedate, 
    assignee,
    CASE
        WHEN duedate IS NULL THEN 'NO DEADLINE'
        WHEN julianday(duedate) < julianday('2026-01-02') THEN 'OVERDUE'
        WHEN julianday(duedate) = julianday('2026-01-02') THEN 'DUE TODAY'
        ELSE 'ON TRACK'
    END AS deadline_status
FROM issues
WHERE duedate IS NOT NULL AND julianday(duedate) >= julianday('2026-01-02')
ORDER BY duedate;
